7 An Act relating to community health workers; creating
the Oklahoma Community Health Worker Act; providing
8 short title; defining terms; directing establishment
of certificate; making certification voluntary;
9 listing functions of community health worker;
requiring and prohibiting certain acts by community
10 health worker; providing eligibility criteria;
directing promulgation of certain rules; providing
11 for codification; and providing an effective date.
12
13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 2063a of Title 63, unless there
17 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 This act shall be known and may be cited as the “Oklahoma
19 Community Health Worker Act”.
20 SECTION 2. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
21 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 2063b of Title 63, unless there
22 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
23 As used in the Oklahoma Community Health Worker Act:
24
